  <brief_title>Measuring the Incidence of Hospital Readmissions Based on Adverse Drug Events</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measuring the Incidence of Hospital Readmissions, Caused by Adverse Drug Events (ADE) Due to Anticoagulants in Vzw Jessa Hospital (Belgium)</official_title>
